{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1679-06_031","@resp":"mercure","head":{"value":"Le Moineau et l’Hirondelle. Fable.","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", juin 1679 [tome 6], p. 31-36.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"#1":{"value":"Tout le monde n’aime pas avec la mesme fidelité que le Chevalier dont je vous parle, &amp; il en est peu qui ne trouvassent enfin quelque dégoust à ne voir jamais que le mesme Objet. La Fable du Moineau en est une preuve. Elle est traitée par M","id":"/div/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" Brossard de Montanay. Vous connoissez son talent à tourner agreablement les choses.","id":"/div/p/#2"}},"quote":{"label":[{"@type":"head","#1":{"value":"Le Moineau","id":"/div/quote/label[0]/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"et l’Hirondelle.","id":"/div/quote/label[0]/#2"}},{"@type":"head","#":{"value":"Fable.","id":"/div/quote/label[1]/#"}}],"l":["L'Hyver cédoit à peine à la saison nouvelle,","Lors qu’un Moineau qui couroit sur les tois,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[2]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[2]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Vit arriver une Hirondelle ;","id":"/div/quote/l[2]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[3]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[3]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Il l’avoit connuë autrefois.","id":"/div/quote/l[3]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[4]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[4]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Dieu vous gard, luy dit-il, la Belle,","id":"/div/quote/l[4]/#"}},"Comment vous va ? depuis pres de six mois",{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[6]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"En ce Païs on ne vous a point veuë.","id":"/div/quote/l[6]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[7]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[7]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Où vous estes-vous donc tenuë ?","id":"/div/quote/l[7]/#"}},"Dans le creux de quelque Arbre ? ou dans le fonds d’un Bois ?",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[9]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[9]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Vous moquez-vous, repartit-elle ?","id":"/div/quote/l[9]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[10]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"A vostre avis j’ay donc l’air d’un Hybou ?","id":"/div/quote/l[10]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[11]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[11]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"J'irois me cacher dans un trou !","id":"/div/quote/l[11]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[12]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[12]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Je n’ay pas si peu de cervelle.","id":"/div/quote/l[12]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[13]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[13]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Ces superbes Maisons des Champs,","id":"/div/quote/l[13]/#"}},"Et tous ces grands Hostels qu’on bastit à la Ville,","Ne sont-ils pas à moy ? Quand je viens au Printemps,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[16]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[16]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"N'en fais-je pas mon domicile,","id":"/div/quote/l[16]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[17]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[17]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Et croyez-vous de bonne-foy","id":"/div/quote/l[17]/#"}},"Que lors que d’un Hyver les rigueurs effroyables",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[19]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[19]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Vous rendent icy misérables,","id":"/div/quote/l[19]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[20]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[20]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Ce malheur s’étende sur moy ?","id":"/div/quote/l[20]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[21]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[21]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Eh pourquoy non ? quel rare privilege","id":"/div/quote/l[21]/#"}},"Vous rend, dit le Moineau, moins frileuse que nous ?","Quand la terre en ces lieux est couverte de neige,","Un Soleil fait exprés ne luit-il que pour vous ?",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[25]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[25]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Vous remplumez-vous ? bagatelle,","id":"/div/quote/l[25]/#"}},"C'est n’est point tout cela, mais suivant la saison","Je change de Païs, &amp; c’est là ma finesse,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[28]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[28]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Je n’y fais point d’autre façon.","id":"/div/quote/l[28]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[29]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[29]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Si vous aviez moins de paresse,","id":"/div/quote/l[29]/#"}},"Et si las de passer la saison des frimas",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[31]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[31]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"A vivre comme un misérable","id":"/div/quote/l[31]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[32]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[32]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Sous les tuiles d’un Galétas,","id":"/div/quote/l[32]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[33]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[33]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Vous cherchiez en d’autres climas","id":"/div/quote/l[33]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[34]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[34]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Une saison plus favorable,","id":"/div/quote/l[34]/#"}},"Vous auriez comme moy des jours toûjours heureux.",{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[36]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"L'Eté finy, vous iriez en Provence,","id":"/div/quote/l[36]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[37]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[37]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Où nous rencontrerions tous deux","id":"/div/quote/l[37]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[38]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[38]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Un beau Printemps qui recommence.","id":"/div/quote/l[38]/#"}},"Fort bien, dit le Moineau, j’aime assez le Printemps.","Et du grain pour manger ? Du grain ? belle demande !",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[41]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[41]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Le Mil est par tout dans les Champs,","id":"/div/quote/l[41]/#"}},"Et l’on en prend sans qu’aucun le défende.","Tant-mieux ; j’y deviendray plus dodu qu’un Chapon,",{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[44]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"Je l’aime fort, mais s’y divertit-on ?","id":"/div/quote/l[44]/#"}},"Eh vrayment oüy, l’on chante, on se promeine,",{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[46]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"On fait l’amour. Comment ? vous moquez-vous ?","id":"/div/quote/l[46]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[47]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"L'amour ! à qui ? vous voila fort en peine.","id":"/div/quote/l[47]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[48]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"En ce Païs à qui le faisons-nous ?","id":"/div/quote/l[48]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[49]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"N'avons-nous pas chacun une Femelle ?","id":"/div/quote/l[49]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[50]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"Dans la Provence elle nous suit aussy,","id":"/div/quote/l[50]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[51]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[51]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Et nous y faisons avec elle","id":"/div/quote/l[51]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[52]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[52]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"L'amour comme on le fait icy.","id":"/div/quote/l[52]/#"}},"Oh oh, dit le Moineau, cecy change l’affaire.",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[54]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[54]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Quoy, dans ce Païs éloigné,","id":"/div/quote/l[54]/#"}},"De la mesme Femelle on est accompagné ?",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[56]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[56]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Le voyage auroit pû me plaire,","id":"/div/quote/l[56]/#"}},"Mais pour le coup je ne vous suivray pas.",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[58]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[58]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Vous passez donc ainsi la vie ?","id":"/div/quote/l[58]/#"}},"Par tout du mesme Objet vous avez l’embarras ?","Le Mil, ny le Printemps, ne me font plus d’envie,","Je veux estre plumé, si j’en fais un seul pas."]}}}